snippet.title: Batography Trailer
snippet.description: Your ambitions in lunar photography begin here! Play as a curious bat on his mission to take a full fledged photo of the moon. Run, Climb, Glide and Snap your way through an array of obstacles while interacting with the cheeky characters in the neighbourhood. Can you collect all five moon cakes? Say cheese! ...or don't. But hey, they say moon is made of cheese!
